spirit:component.spirit:name: ipcore_add_u30b
spirit:component.spirit:description: The Xilinx LogiCORE Adder Subtracter can create adders, subtracters, and adders/subtracters that operate on signed or unsigned data. In fabric, the module supports inputs ranging from 1 to 256 bits wide, and outputs ranging from 1 to 258 bits wide. I/O widths are family dependent for dsp48 implementations.
